                <a href="http://www.wired.com/category/gamelife/">
                    <img class="img-responsive img-hover" src="images/blog1.jpg" alt="blog image">
                </a>
                <hr>
                <p>Game Life blog is part of the always awesome Wired network. Just like each and everyone of the Wired blogs, GameLife also features in depth articles with high quality content. Extensive interviews with game developers and comprehensive reviews with high resolution screenshots are highlights of this blog.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://www.wired.com/category/gamelife/">Read More <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i></a>

