                <p><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> Posted on October 23, 2015 at 10:45 PM</p>
                <hr>
                <a href="http://www.ign.com/">
                    <img class="img-responsive img-hover" src="images/blog2.jpg" alt="blog image">
                </a>
                <hr>
                <p>FPS Videogamer blog is dedicated only to First Person Shooting games. Popular games like Halo, Call of Duty, Medal of Honor etc. are FPS games and the blog covers those among other similar titles. The blog is quite young and has been around for just six months but has content posted at regular intervals. They have exclusive blogs for Modern Warfare 2 and Call of Duty: Black Ops in their network as well...</p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://www.ign.com/">Read More <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i></a>

