                <a href="blog-post.html">
                    <img class="img-responsive img-hover" src="images/blog3.png" alt="blog mage">
                </a>
                <hr>
                <p>When Giant Bomb claims to be the world’s largest editable video game database, they aren’t lying. With Wiki like actions, users can actually edit the content of a large portion of the content posted in the site. If you are a fan of Anime or comics, do check out their sister blogs in the network. ...</p>
